==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gatepost
<hw>Gate"post`</hw> <pr>(g⟦amac⟧t"p⟦omac⟧st`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A post to which a gate is hung; -- called also
<altname>swinging post</altname> <it>or</it> <altname>hinging
post</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A post against which a gate closes; -- called also
<altname>shutting post</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gateway</ent>⟦br⟧
